          "slidecontent": "• Clinical decision support systems (CDSS) are becoming standard tools across NHS and private healthcare settings\n• This course focuses on one critical question: where should AI assistance stop\n• Designed for clinicians, nurses, and allied health professionals new to working alongside these systems\n• No prior technical knowledge required\n• You will leave with clear, practical boundaries you can apply in your daily practice\n• Real-world scenarios throughout to ground every concept in clinical reality"
